#home
    header
        img(src="/img/header.svg")

    p
        | Bienvenue sur LaBanane, l'application pour écouter et partager votre musique !
        br
        | N'hésitez pas à nous rejoindre sur Facebook pour être tenu au courant des nouveautés, nous remonter un bug ou tout
        | simplement pour partager votre playlist !

    nav
        ul
            li(ng-class="{'selected':isPlaylistSearch}", ng-click='searchPlaylistMode()') Search
            li(ng-class="{'selected':isPlaylistCreation}", ng-click='createPlaylistMode()') Create

    section.search(ng-show='isPlaylistSearch')

        .input-container
            input#input-search-playlist(input-text, type="text", ng-model="search", autocomplete="off")
            label(for="input-search-playlist") Name
        ul.playlists
            li(ng-repeat="playlist in allPlaylists | filter:search")
                a(href="/player/{{playlist}}") {{playlist}}

        h3 Last visited playlists
        ul.playlists
            li(ng-repeat="playlist in lastPlaylists")
                a(href="/player/{{playlist}}") {{playlist}}

    section.create(ng-show='isPlaylistCreation')

        p /!\ Please note that you will not be able to retrieve your password if you lost it !
        .input-container
            input#playlist-name(ng-model="playlistId", input-text, type="text", autocomplete="off")

            label(for="playlist-name") Playlist name
        .input-container
            input#playlist-password(ng-model="playlistPassword", input-text, type="password", autocomplete="off")
            label(for="playlist-password") Password
        button.button(ng-click='createPlaylist()') Create

